
common flags
CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug
CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=$DESTDIR
CMAKE_C_FLAGS_DEBUG="-g -O0"
CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS_DEBUG="-g -O0"

To disable optimization:
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug

To change installation location:
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=$DESTDIR "$@"

To use ninja for the generator
cmake "${path?}" -GNinja


According to ChatGPT, you can tweak at install time with:
cmake --install --prefix
instead of 'make install'.  Have not yet tested.  Also, should be able
to do:
cmake --install --component ...

or

DESTDIR=${PREFIX?} cmake --install $builddir

instead of 'make install'
